All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
API
The class that the user interacts with to get the functionality of the API.
Component
Parent class of all components
ComponentFactory
Concrete class for Factory Design Pattern for creating component object
ComponentNetlistFactory
Concrete class for Factory Design Pattern to create Netlist DTO object based on component type and JSONObject contents
Controller
The class that the API calls as it contains the implementation of the required methods.
IComponentFactory
Interface for Factory Design Pattern for creating component objects based on the type
IComponentNetlistFactory
Interface for Factory Design Pattern for creating a Component Netlist DTO
